verbose_text: Of note was the fact this line expressed higher levels of Oct4, Sox2, Klf4, Gjb5 and Scpep1, which suggests that despite an initial destabilisation of the pluripotent state (lower levels of Oct4, Sox2 and Nanog at the protein level), this line progressively stabilised in a ' higher-naive ' state (XREF_FIG C).
evidence: levels of Oct4, Sox2, Klf4, Gjb5
